{"tid":96071,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"37歲甘比逾400億身家 膺香港女首富No.1","createTime":"2017-01-26T13:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T14:42:00.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f8f2ca05d4e3fbee9bdc8270d1f300b5810e58c","tid":96071,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170126/large/1485436319_bad8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170126%2Flarge%2F1485436319_bad8.jpg&h=876a7ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年剛出爐嘅福布斯香港50大富豪榜，排名第一嘅香港女首富係人稱「殼后」、金利豐行政總裁朱李月華(新聞連結： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2jAlZvX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2jAlZvX&d=Eo4Nhmzh%2FDEa4pw63Qb4Y5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=df365186\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2jAlZvX</a> )，朱太今年身家有48億美元(約374億元)，排全港首富第14位。不過依家香港女首富之位，已由甘比陳凱韻以逾400億身家、力壓朱太膺no.1，更超過人稱「細劉」、排名37位擁120億身家嘅劉鑾鴻。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170126/large/1485433746_00cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170126%2Flarge%2F1485433746_00cf.jpg&h=86557c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大劉給予甘比50億現備用打官司。<br />\n<br />\n緊接朱太之後嘅香港女首富排名，重新洗牌第三就係何超瓊(335億身家)；第四位係賭王四太梁安琪(312億)。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170126/large/1485433678_e18f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170126%2Flarge%2F1485433678_e18f.jpg&h=af054b1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n甘比去年12月正式成為「劉太」，萬千寵愛在一身，之前大劉已不斷大量送贈現金、物業畀對方，物業記者落水扮美人魚，點知變咗做鯉魚王～ #彈吓彈吓 🙈🙈包括如中半山帝景園、山頂歌賦山里道獨立屋、灣仔壹環、鰂魚涌太古城及將軍澳中心多個物業，以及高士美道大宅，估計16億。加上大劉曾送贈分別名為「The Sweet Josephine」、「The Blue Moon of Josephine」、「Star of Josephine」名鑽畀大女秀樺，當時買入價合共6.64億，估計o依家升值唔少。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170126/large/1485433418_b6f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170126%2Flarge%2F1485433418_b6f7.jpg&h=17bad67b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n甘比所有禮物，全部都係億億聲計，加埋大劉今日親證送咗市值180億嘅尖沙嘴The ONE，保守估計甘比身家已暴升至400億，令由記者出身比嘅甘比一夜之間以37歲之齡成為最後生嘅香港女首富。<br />\n<br />\n甘比新贈身家清單：<br />\nThe ONE商廈 180億<br />\n大劉給甘比備用打官司現金　 50億<br />\n20億美金美國債劵 約156億<br />\n深水灣3號獨立屋 13億<br />\n肇輝臺12號項目 15億"},{"pid":"a90d2cdf71ba363aa33df6fe42c3787f45a9a021","tid":96071,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd446104f66ae582ae181329cc3d2cebc42efdd8","tid":96071,"uid":71000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:58:42.000Z","msg":"甘比好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a43965ec7fb0c661886a233865c24279c4cdb02","tid":96071,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:59:42.000Z","msg":"相比許晉亭佢真係好撚窮"},{"pid":"eff235f61c87c0da0183a2ce94494b38cd040e92","tid":96071,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:01:56.000Z","msg":"關我地d窮撚撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19787ee3cf858db24dad52186e2dc295a2d245e1","tid":96071,"uid":11914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:02:58.000Z","msg":"共通點就係全部都唔係靠自己， 做女人真好"},{"pid":"779bdd40c089bbf60bfe36803b2c11229f6a3b91","tid":96071,"uid":7288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:05:24.000Z","msg":"真係幸運"},{"pid":"3a46c5033b4290b9859b1cf853b4256036f4bad0","tid":96071,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c346ca475ac134d4e308aec1f07d